==English==
===Etymology===
from Greek: ''[[ίππος]]'' horse + ''[[δρόμος]]'' ([[-drome]]) a course

===Noun===
'''hippodrome'''
# a place of entertainment: [[theatre]], [[circus]], [[dancehall]]
# a horse racing course

